  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation
By: Ibn 'Atâ'illâh
---
More fearing are the gnostics in a state of spiritual expansion (bast)
than they are in contraction (qabd), for few are those in the state of
expansion who stay within the confines of spiritual propriety (adab).
